  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill Up is a satisfying 3D Jump & Run experience with a stage based progression system. In each stage, you must reach the goal without falling down! Each stage comes with a unique concept and hurdles that have to be mastered. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong>: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A large variety of colorful, unique stages. Stages contain classic platformer elements and other unique mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfectly synchronized systems that behave identically on every run. Speed running has never been fairer or easier! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional mastery: After completing a stage, it can be played again to master it. This time, you shall not stop moving until reaching the goal! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill Up is a satisfying 3D Jump & Run experience with a stage based progression system. In each stage, you must reach the goal without falling down! Each stage comes with a unique concept and hurdles that have to be mastered. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong>: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A large variety of colorful, unique stages. Stages contain classic platformer elements and other unique mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfectly synchronized systems that behave identically on every run. Speed running has never been fairer or easier! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional mastery: After completing a stage, it can be played again to master it. This time, you shall not stop moving until reaching the goal! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
